query:
SELECT 
  sci.id,
  sci.productSku,
  sci.productName,
  sci.expectedQuantity,
  sci.checkedQuantity,
  sci.divergence,
  (sci.checkedQuantity - sci.expectedQuantity) as calculated_div
FROM stageChecks sc
JOIN stageCheckItems sci ON sc.id = sci.stageCheckId
WHERE sc.status = 'divergent'
ORDER BY sc.id DESC, sci.id
LIMIT 10;
